title: TehomAt - Demonic History and the Rites of Exorcism - David P. A
description:
"TehomAt - Demonic History and the Rites of Exorcism" is a book that, as the title suggests, deals with the recorded history of demons from a variety of sources, including the Hebrew Scriptures, Sanskrit texts, Babylonian legends, and Egyptian mythology. 

Providing insights into such concepts as what makes demons "tick" and paranormal phenomenon such as telekinesis and hauntings, the book, authored by David P. Aguilar Jr. PhD, also delves into the mechanics of possession - and thus the concept of exorcism.
